    "description_long": "This object is a blocky, stylized machine gun with a compact, angular silhouette, reminiscent of a submachine gun or compact assault weapon. The main body is rectangular with a stepped top rail, and a prominent, squared-off barrel extends from the front. The grip is thick and geometric, positioned below the main receiver, and a short, boxy stock is attached at the rear. The magazine is not distinctly visible, suggesting it may be integrated or not modeled in detail. The entire object is rendered in a dark, nearly black color, giving it a monolithic and utilitarian appearance.",
